data.description: Beautifully maintained new home in the vibrant heart of New Braunfels! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence is nestled in a new and thriving neighborhood with easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment. Alternatively, enjoy your own private backyard haven, perfect for enjoying with guests or quiet evenings under the stars. The home has endless opportunities and offers the perfect blend of modern comfort with a charming community atmosphere.
